    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just dont want to keep running to the doctor every time i want to tweak my vitamins or something. my doctor was super vague about it. like, if my blood work has been stable for months, wouldnt a lower dose just be a way to test if my body cant handle the 5mg anymore? it seems safer than overdoing it on the meds.",
